Package com.github.cwilper.fcrepo.store.util.commands

Defines the Command interface and built-in implementations.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Command An executable command.
 

Class Summary
BatchObjectCommand Base class for Commands that work with multiple FedoraObjects in a FedoraStoreSession.
CommandContext Provides ThreadLocal data relevant to the currently-executing Command.
CopyCommand Copies FedoraObjects from one FedoraStore to another.
DeleteCommand Deletes FedoraObjects in a given FedoraStore.
FilteringBatchObjectCommand Base class for BatchObjectCommands that also perform filtering.
ListCommand Lists each FedoraObjects in the given FedoraStore.
ModifyCommand Modifies FedoraObjects in a given FedoraStore.
